href="gr-000G.xml"
addr="gr-000G"
title="Group">Group</fr:link>. We define the <html:dfn
xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Center</html:dfn> of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[G]]></fr:tex> to be the <fr:link
type="local"
href="gr-001B.xml"
addr="gr-001B"
title="Subgroup">Subgroup</fr:link> <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[Z(G)]]></fr:tex> of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[G]]></fr:tex> consisting of all elements which commute with all of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[G]]></fr:tex>: for any <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[z\in  G]]></fr:tex>, we have <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[z\in  Z(G)]]></fr:tex> if and only if for every <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[g\in  G]]></fr:tex> we have <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[zg=gz]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
 
   
